為了避免程式和資料的冗餘問題，應該善用繼承的機制。相同的資料或動作可藉由proetced 宣告，給子類別繼承使用。
不變的物件資料要宣告在Letter的抽象類別裡
所以要加入
protected String title ,receiver ,content ,sender ,date;
    Letter(String title, String receiver, String content, String sender, String date)
    {
        this.title = title;
        this.receiver =receiver ;
        this.content = content;
        this.sender = sender;
        this.date =date ;
    }
    public String getSender()
    {
        return sender;
    }
    public String getReceiver()
    {
        return receiver;
    }        
    public String getDate()
    {
        return date;
    }
